    "description": {
      "value": "<p>You bless up all allied creatures of your choice within range. Whenever a target lands a successful hit before the spell ends, the target can add 1 to the damage roll.<br>When cast by multiple casters chanting in unison, the same increases to 2 points added to the damage roll.<br><em><strong>At Higher Levels.</strong></em> When you cast this spell using a spell slot of 3rd level or higher, you can extend the range by 10 feet for each slot level above 2nd.<br>Content licensed under the @UUID[Compendium.koboldpressogl.koboldpressjournal.JournalEntry.KoboldPressOGL00.JournalEntryPage.KoboldPressOGLpg]{Open Game License}",
